                "institute": "2NEDKVI"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Experiments performed at the AGOR",
                "cyclotron at KVI, Groningen using the Big-Bite",
                "Spectrometer and seven large-volume high-purity",
                "germanium detectors"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MAGSP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " QQD-type BBT spectrometer with focal plane",
                "detectors, angular acceptance of up to 13 msr and a",
                "K value of 430 MeV, was used to analyse scattered",
                "alpha particles"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COIN",
                "MWDC",
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The light-ion detection system",
                "consisting of two vertical drift chambers and two",
                "scintillator planes was used in focal plane of BBT",
                "spectrometer to determine position and angles of",
                "scattered alpha particles."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "To detect the subsequent gamma ray emission,",
                "seven HPGe detectors were positioned with an",
                "entrance window distance of about 23 cm to the",
                "target.Each detector has a relative efficiency of",
                "about 100%, four detectors were surrounded with",
                "bismuth germanate (BGO) shields for active",
                "background suppression. The total photopeak",
                "efficiency of the array was about 0.45%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COINC",
                "TOF",
                "ASPEC",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Time of flight with respect to",
                "cyclotron HF was used to reduce background in HPGe",
                "detectors"
              ]
            }
